{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">A casual and relaxing game for those who like Christmas themes or Lofi music, the game has an easy yet challenging difficulty, being able to play both by levels and in infinite mode where the object is always to get more points.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The game features simple mechanics. To move the pieces horizontally, you need to use the left or right arrow keys, rotate the piece with the up arrow, speed up the movement with the down arrow key, and with the space key, you can instantly position the piece.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2221260/extras/TutorialImagem.png?t=1732380794\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Stage Mode: The objective is to complete the challenges that appear in each level to go to the next one, until you finish all the levels.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Infinite Mode: The goal is to get as many points as possible, there is no time limit or points, the player can spend hours getting more points.</p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2221260/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1732380794","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2221260/page_bg_generated.jpg?t=1732380794","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2221260/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1732380794","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2221260/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1732380794","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Family Sharing","id":62}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"detailed_description":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">A casual and relaxing game for those who like Christmas themes or Lofi music, the game has an easy yet challenging difficulty, being able to play both by l